  "notes": [
    "v864-3 is a WebView (HTML/JS) re-implementation of v864-2 (Tkinter). The heavyweight OneStopInboundDialog (4302 lines, 4 file-upload slots + B/L/PL/Invoice/D/O parsing + preview table + undo/redo) has been reduced to a single generic _showPdfUploadModal helper (103 lines, 1 file slot).",
